Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:01:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Location of the Finals - Alcatraz"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I apologize, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll give your body back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah... What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going back to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was only for a short while, but I got a real body again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't go, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I've been able\N to get my heart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all thanks to you, Mokuba. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to get a hold of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to live in\N the Real World for Noah, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And to do that, I can't rely on my big brother all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It's the pitiful wreckage symbolizing Gozaburo's remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island, Alcatraz, was built as a military industrial facility by Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atop the wreckage stands the Duel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the final battlefield for this Battle City Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come to settle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik holds the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi holds Osiris the Heaven Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hold Obelisk the Great War God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one to obtain all three cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as stand atop the Duel Tower in victory, will be {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Alcatraz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The climax of this fight is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Mai's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik, what the hell did you do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we speak, that woman is falling deeper and deeper into darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll wander in immeasurable loneliness, doomed to never regain conscious again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you {\b0}defeat{\b1} me, there's a {\i1}chance{\i0} she'll recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick Malik's sorry ass and save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, you've got to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's finally begun... the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear sister, you lost so soon in this fight that you have the pleasure of quietly watching from the sidelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a care in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Rishid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb with {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so {\i1}obvious{\i0} that you were the one who hid him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I {\i1}did{\i0} know, there's no way I would ever tell {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd act this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this is one of them.\N This originally belonged to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave your Millennium Tauk to the Pharaoh, did you {\i1}not{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written {\i1}all over{\i0} your face right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to fend off this Millennium Rod with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a {\i1}simple task{\i0} for me to brainwash you and take my time having you tell me where Rishid is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}love{\i0} that look of fear on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would see you making that face, dear sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time for such acts of pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention! We are about to arrive at Alcatraz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All participating Duelists should prepare their decks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rishid was struck by the wrath of Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be all that easy to wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, he may {\i1}never{\i0} wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're waiting for Kaiba or Yugi to save the day, you may as well save the effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the Ra I hold, all that awaits them is {\i1}failure{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now them, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I'm done crushing the Pharaoh in the upcoming Duels, I'll take my {\i1}sweet time{\i0} killing Rishid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear sister, you had better keep your mouth shut and watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch as the little hope you have left is swallowed by the darkness of death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} really disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. Bakura lost to Malik's Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyone who loses a Dark Game won't return until the one who created it is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So {\b0}you{\b1} came here, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did you send Bakura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who knows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody {\b0}knows{\b1} where those who lose a Dark Game are sent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been so many sacrifices in these Duels...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of this happened because of the memory I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's sacrificing those who own Millennium Items or who are involved in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He wants to bury everything in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of it is my-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong! You're not at fault here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be responsible for memories you don't even remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you always trying to protect everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there still might be a way to save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you go giving up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All we can do is go forward bravely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We wouldn't be True Duelists if we gave up in the middle of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been looking for you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to arrive at our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're here, I wonder where Bakura went off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll be alright with those wounds he had...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope he's not being controlled by the Millennium Ring again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0} will be back before you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! We just gotta believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! It's time to go, Duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you permission to step into my fortress of pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the location of the Final, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's so big! It almost seems to go straight through the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! This is a battleground where Duelists battle for their place at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}I'll{\i0} be the one standing at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! Don't forget about {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm done kicking {\i1}your{\i0} ass,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll know that you're nothing but the king of this {\i1}rubble{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll end up on the {\i1}scrapheap{\i0} of Duelist history, you deadbeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go bury\N yourself in the ruins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You know...! I'm {\i1}also{\i0} one of the final participants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Relax{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! You'll settle things in the Duels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere here really puts you on edge, doesn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, {\i1}his majesty{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malik! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OOH-AH!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda... you're {\i1}still{\i0}\N talking like a monkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mr. host!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided the order of battle for the Semi-Finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold your horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out what's gonna happen when you get to the tower and learn your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By {\i1}fate{\i0}, I presume you mean all of your {\i1}losses{\i0} and {\i1}deaths{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Duelists and observers, welcome to Duel Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now hold the Battle City Tournament Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how exactly are they going to Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four remaining Duelists
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will head to the top of the tower through four different doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four doors...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please choose one out of the four doors presented before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the doors give one any sort of advantage in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say that,\N it's still hard to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one are you gonna pick, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with either one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...! "Eeny, meeny, miny, moe..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An indecisive, {\i1}deadbeat{\i0} fool like yourself can just take whichever one is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"...catch a tiger by the toe... If he hollers let him go,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Eeny, meeny, miny, moe!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! I pick that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I just picked that door, ya jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, I'm heading in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess this is the only one left...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're headed this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, sometimes the last one is the {\i1}luckiest{\i0} one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... a Card Battle System?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they're up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's so high, you can't see the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna do this inside here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, how are the match-ups going to be decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is about to be decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Kaiba! Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet already! It's about to be explained so even a deadbeat can understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! Wanna say that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For proud Duelists such as yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be {\i1}unfair{\i0} to decide your opponents with a mere {\i1}lottery{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Semi-Finals shall be decided with a {\i1}game{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Decide our opponents for the Semi-Finals with a game...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a four-way Duel between the remaining Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first two to arrive at the top...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as the two\N remaining at the bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be paired up for the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning... it's a four-person Battle Royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course the game will be Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will start with 4,000 Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you lose Life Points, your gondolas\N will climb higher and higher toward the top of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the two who lose first will be the first to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each player will use your regular 40-card deck which you prepared for the game tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuffle it and set it in the Duel Disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you connect your Duel Disk to the gondola,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your cards, as well as the other players', will be displayed on the viewing screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All four players will take separate turns,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may attack any player you choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first two Duelists who rise to the top will be in the first match of the Semi-Finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a lot better than I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the outcome of this match has nothing to do with the tournament rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most important Duel of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Otogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means you get to choose the opponent you want to Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, let's say Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} wants to fight Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} first in the Semi-Finals,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other two could end up {\i1}supporting{\i0} Yugi so {\i1}they{\i0} can fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the other hand, the two could gang up on him and attack all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this Battle Royale is all about who you crush first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means the\N first person they'd go after...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are {\i1}you{\i0} staring at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey man, do your best so you don't lose in the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking all kinds of crap down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The objective of this game is to split us into pairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With good strategy, it should be possible to choose your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.28,0:15:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who do I want to fight\N in the Semi-Finals?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one person it can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik's Ra card has overwhelming power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to beat him, I'm going to need two God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So my opponent for these Semi-Finals has to be the other God Card wielder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponent, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi... I've wanted to kill you for {\b0}so{\b1} long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi! I got this far in Battle City because I want to fight {\b0}you{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, when I win this tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when the time comes where I can call myself a True Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When that time comes, please fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll fight each other then, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}, I'll wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take care of your Red-Eyes until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remember our promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I haven't forgotten about my Red-Eyes you're holding onto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to fight you in order to get him back! And I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.03,0:16:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to save Mai, I've got to beat {\b0}him{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now decide who goes first and the order of play amongst the four of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each player must choose one Monster Card from your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever has the highest Attack Power takes the first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that Monster Card must be removed from your deck for the duration of this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have to sacrifice a Monster with high Attack Power in order to go first...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you get the initiative, you can strike the first blow against any opponent you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're bound to take\N the lead by doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Getting the upper hand is worth it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mind games have begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now please present your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a card I got as an ante...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care if I lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got the first strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't wanna give up any of my cards with high Attack Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The order has been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba will be taking the first turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Malik Ishtar...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Katsuya Jounouchi in the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's two players to avoid in the Semi-Finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to make sure they end up fighting each other in the first game...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that {\b0}deadbeat{\b1} who's not even a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a Duelist, I want to fight Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to so bad, I can taste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who should I fight against?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you having trouble deciding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, to be honest, I'm having trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have many reasons to fight all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's a few objectives I have to fulfill!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It says of the Pharaoh "You will know him by the three God Cards he wields."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, the one who collects the three God Cards will be crowned the title "Pharaoh"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and regain the Millennium Items and his lost memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to regain my memories, I must face my true enemy, Malik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time we'll fight each other fair and square, as True Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My promise to Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this final tournament, we are about to step foot into the domain of the gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner will be {\b0}determined{\b1} by the three God Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}will{\b1} beat you and Malik, obtain the three God Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and become the world's strongest Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fated battle with Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have more than enough reasons to fight all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup! In that case, just fight whoever you feel you must!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person I'm going to fight is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle City Final Match Preliminary Round will be held as a Battle Royale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel start!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place one card face-down and Summon Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't attack\N a player on the first turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as soon as my next turn comes, I'll make my move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My{\i0} turn then, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Newdoria!\N In Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This fiend's Special Ability\N is {\b0}quite{\b1} useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to determine\N the opponent I'll fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll follow the vector\N of my Duelist's soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Big Shield Gardna in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also play two face-down cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hand sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't even have a\N Monster Card to sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:20:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}ecosystem{\i0} of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}food chain{\i0} of battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}weak{\i0} small fry! I'll show you that {\i1}barking dogs{\i0} are no match for a {\i1}lion{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood Vorse! Go ahead and Direct Attack this deadbeat of a nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Jounouchi doesn't have any Wall Monsters to protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap!\N The Regulation of Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chosen Type selected by this Trap Card cannot attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Tribe-Type I've chosen is the Beast-Warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.21,0:21:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've chosen to fulfill the promise I made to my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Battle Royale is meant to determine the match-ups for the Semi-Finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the selected four battle it out viciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi intends to keep his promise with Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jounouchi intends to face Malik in order to save Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} aims to face Yugi so he can win his Osiris and use it to fight Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Malik intends to kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, the Duel soars towards its climax!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Battle Royale!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.45,0:23:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.54,0:23:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
